{
  "number": 56,
  "name": "سُورَةُ الوَاقِعَةِ",
  "englishName": "Al-Waaqia",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "When the event befalleth -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "There is no denying that it will befall -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "Abasing (some), exalting (others);",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "When the earth is shaken with a shock",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "And the hills are ground to powder",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "So that they become a scattered dust,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "And ye will be three kinds:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "(First) those on the right hand; what of those on the right hand?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "And (then) those on the left hand; what of those on the left hand?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "And the foremost in the race, the foremost in the race:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "Those are they who will be brought nigh",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "In gardens of delight;",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "A multitude of those of old",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "And a few of those of later time.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "On lined couches,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Reclining therein face to face.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 534,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "There wait on them immortal youths",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "With bowls and ewers and a cup from a pure spring",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "Wherefrom they get no aching of the head nor any madness,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "And fruit that they prefer",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "And flesh of fowls that they desire.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "And (there are) fair ones with wide, lovely eyes,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "Like unto hidden pearls,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "Reward for what they used to do.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "There hear they no vain speaking nor recrimination",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "(Naught) but the saying: Peace, (and again) Peace.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "And those on the right hand; what of those on the right hand?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "Among thornless lote-trees",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "And clustered plantains,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "And spreading shade,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "And water gushing,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "And fruit in plenty",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "Neither out of reach nor yet forbidden,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "And raised couches;",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "Lo! We have created them a (new) creation",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "And made them virgins,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 37,
      "text": "Lovers, friends,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 38,
      "text": "For those on the right hand;",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 469,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 39,
      "text": "A multitude of those of old",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 40,
      "text": "And a multitude of those of later time.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 41,
      "text": "And those on the left hand: What of those on the left hand?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 42,
      "text": "In scorching wind and scalding water",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 43,
      "text": "And shadow of black smoke,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 44,
      "text": "Neither cool nor refreshing.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 45,
      "text": "Lo! heretofore they were effete with luxury",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 46,
      "text": "And used to persist in the awful sin.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 47,
      "text": "And they used to say: When we are dead and have become dust and bones, shall we then, forsooth, be raised again,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 48,
      "text": "And also our forefathers?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 49,
      "text": "Say (unto them, O Muhammad): Lo! those of old and those of later time",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 50,
      "text": "Will all be brought together to the tryst of an appointed day.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 535,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 51,
      "text": "Then lo! ye, the erring, the deniers,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 52,
      "text": "Ye verily will eat of a tree called Zaqqum",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 53,
      "text": "And will fill your bellies therewith;",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 54,
      "text": "And thereon ye will drink of boiling water,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 55,
      "text": "Drinking even as the camel drinketh.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 56,
      "text": "This will be their welcome on the Day of Judgment.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 57,
      "text": "We created you. Will ye then admit the truth?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 58,
      "text": "Have ye seen that which ye emit?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 59,
      "text": "Do ye create it or are We the Creator?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 60,
      "text": "We mete out death among you, and We are not to be outrun,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 61,
      "text": "That We may transfigure you and make you what ye know not.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 62,
      "text": "And verily ye know the first creation. Why, then, do ye not reflect?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 63,
      "text": "Have ye seen that which ye cultivate?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 64,
      "text": "Is it ye who foster it, or are We the Fosterer?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 65,
      "text": "If We willed, We verily could make it chaff, then would ye cease not to exclaim:",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 66,
      "text": "Lo! we are laden with debt!",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 67,
      "text": "Nay, but we are deprived!",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 68,
      "text": "Have ye observed the water which ye drink?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 69,
      "text": "Is it ye who shed it from the raincloud, or are We the Shedder?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 70,
      "text": "If We willed We verily could make it bitter. Why then, give ye not thanks?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 71,
      "text": "Have ye observed the fire which ye strike out;",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 72,
      "text": "Was it ye who made the tree thereof to grow, or were We the grower?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 73,
      "text": "We, even We, appointed it a memorial and a comfort for the dwellers in the wilderness.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 74,
      "text": "Therefor (O Muhammad), praise the name of thy Lord, the Tremendous.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 470,
      "hizbQuarter": 214,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 75,
      "text": "Nay, I swear by the places of the stars -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 76,
      "text": "And lo! that verily is a tremendous oath, if ye but knew -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 536,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 77,
      "text": "That (this) is indeed a noble Qur'an",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 78,
      "text": "In a Book kept hidden",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 79,
      "text": "Which none toucheth save the purified,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 80,
      "text": "A revelation from the Lord of the Worlds.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 81,
      "text": "Is it this Statement that ye scorn,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 82,
      "text": "And make denial thereof your livelihood?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 83,
      "text": "Why, then, when (the soul) cometh up to the throat (of the dying)",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 84,
      "text": "And ye are at that moment looking",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 85,
      "text": "- And We are nearer unto him than ye are, but ye see not -",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 86,
      "text": "Why then, if ye are not in bondage (unto Us),",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 87,
      "text": "Do ye not force it back, if ye are truthful?",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 88,
      "text": "Thus if he is of those brought nigh,",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 89,
      "text": "Then breath of life, and plenty, and a Garden of delight.",
      "juz": 27,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 537,
      "ruku": 471,
      "hizbQuarter": 215,
      "sajda": false
